## 12.7. FastF1 Data Ingestion Pipeline

Real F1 data is loaded via the **FastF1 API** with intelligent caching:

```python
# Enable FastF1 cache for efficient data loading
CACHE_DIR = Path("data/cache")
fastf1.Cache.enable_cache(str(CACHE_DIR))

def get_race_results(year: int, round_number: int) -> pd.DataFrame:
    """Fetch race results from FastF1 API."""
    session = fastf1.get_session(year, round_number, "R")
    session.load()
    
    df = pd.DataFrame(session.results)
    df["year"] = year
    df["round"] = round_number
    df["race_name"] = session.event["EventName"]
    return df
```

